::Prowl/Kluster::

-Sure, love,- Prowl replies to Iron Raptor, sensing her slightly 
annoyed state. He activates his comm-link, sending a message to 
Symphony.

"Nice music," he says to the bot, "You can join us I guess. Come to 
my position. You should be able to track this transmission. But be 
careful, a battle has just ended and some bots might still be firing."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Kluster nods, watching Tarantopoulus run off. "Allright. Be careful 
though."
